{"tid":422799,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[空白的一坪]日本持有者不明的土地持續增加","createTime":"2017-10-03T11:19:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-06T00:09:21.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"326da38eb9d96360455e80aa2176e8c36957d090","tid":422799,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T11:19:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/web_tokushu/still/web_tokushu_2017_1003_img_03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww3.nhk.or.jp%2Fnews%2Fweb_tokushu%2Fstill%2Fweb_tokushu_2017_1003_img_03.jpg&h=7f28f1e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原因係登記簿上登錄咗既持有者死亡之後<br />\n繼承土地既人冇去登記簿到更新返 搞到本簿上面土地持有者個名仲係死撚咗個條友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n登記唔係強制性 所以個問題最近越黎越嚴重<br />\n建築物重建或者轉賣土地都要所有繼承人一致同意先得<br />\n是但連絡唔到一個就收得皮  <br />\n<img src=\"http://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/web_tokushu/still/web_tokushu_2017_1003_img_01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww3.nhk.or.jp%2Fnews%2Fweb_tokushu%2Fstill%2Fweb_tokushu_2017_1003_img_01.jpg&h=3d0df69f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以前東日本大震災個陣岩手縣就係因為搵唔到個持有者所以震後復興先會搞到咁遲<br />\n黎緊預定係2027年開業既リニア中央新幹線都遇到相同既問題<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/web_tokushu/2017_1003.html?utm_int=news_contents_news-closeup_002\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww3.nhk.or.jp%2Fnews%2Fweb_tokushu%2F2017_1003.html%3Futm_int%3Dnews_contents_news-closeup_002&d=2IMsTC82ZZRjUYub15B0n5Uc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=d46dc868\" target=\"_blank\">http://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/web_tokushu/2017_1003.html?utm_int=news_contents_news-closeup_002</a>"},{"pid":"6af868116145c2f65b6a43a9b359de14751adc1a","tid":422799,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T18:59:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8c1a55e22a08c92ea1b282b79b5eb9d7708dce","tid":422799,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim